wiki.summary: "Untouched" is the second single by The Veronicas from their sophomore album, Hook Me Up. It was released in December 2007 to Australia. It is also the first single from the same album in North America and Europe. The song is written by Jess and Lisa and also has writing credits from Toby Gad. According to the Untouched Songfacts, the song is "about a long distance relationship and having to interact over the technology of today ."
